headline: /C O R R E C T I O N -- Lennox International Inc./
summary: Lennox (NYSE: LII), a leader in the HVAC industry, is making significant investments in its distribution network and customer service and training capabilities in the Dallas—Fort Worth area. This initiative includes expanding training facilities and distribution infrastructure, reinforcing its commitment to customers and growth acceleration.
